// Link
// Styled anchor that supports external links (opens in new tab) and an onClick override.

FUNCTION handleClick(e)
  IF an onClick prop is provided, prevents default navigation and calls onClick.
  Otherwise allows normal anchor navigation.

---

FUNCTION Link(props) -> ReactNode                                         EXPORT
  Renders an anchor element with the provided href and label.
  IF href starts with "http" or is external, adds target="_blank" and rel="noopener noreferrer".
  Calls handleClick on click.
